Atlassian-EditConfluence

Edit Confluence wikis using Perl!


To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	Build
	Build test
	Build install


Usage:

	use Atlassian::EditConfluence;
	
	my $editor = Atlassian::EditConfluence->new(
		url => 'https://your.wiki.url/rpc/xmlrpc',
		username => 'user123',
		password => 'my secret password',
	);
	
	$editor->editOrCreatePage(
		spaceKey => 'Department12',
		pageTitle => 'Sandbox',
		content => 'It works!',
	);


Read more about the Confluence API here: 

https://developer.atlassian.com/display/CONFDEV/Confluence+XML-RPC+and+SOAP+APIs
